creator: Rent4Me Inc
descriptionHtml:
Rent anything you want! Share unused stuff!

Do you want to earn extra money just by sharing things which you don’t use anymore?
How about building your own business with this simple Application?

You and rent anything you want from your neighbors or from rental companies.
More than 70000 things already listed.
Never renting or lending was so easy.

Still don't trust people? Create your own rental club with your friends.
descriptionShort: This service allows you to rent/lend anything you want from your neighbors.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
- Currencies list was fixed
- Bugfix for Xiaomi phones
